Note:
Runa Standard Library: Date and Time Module

Designed for AI-to-AI interfacing with nanosecond precision, natural language syntax, and comprehensive metadata support.

Idiomatic Runa code uses natural language operators:
  Let now be get current datetime with precision as "nanosecond"
  Let tomorrow be add days to now with count as 1
  Let parsed be parse datetime from "2024-01-15T14:30:25.123456789Z" with format as "iso"
  Let duration be calculate duration between start_time and end_time with precision as "nanosecond"

For advanced/AI-generated code, use helpers:
  Let result be create with year as 2024 and month as 1 and day as 15
  Let result be parse with string as date_string and format as parse_format
:End Note

